thread.title: Divided House Republicans see savior in Paul Ryan

title: Divided House Republicans see savior in Paul Ryan
text:
> Florida Divided House Republicans see savior in Paul Ryan House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy of Calif. walks toward the House Chamber on Capitol Hill in Washington, Friday, Oct. 9, 2015. In the unruly House, Republicans enjoy a near-historic majority, yet deep divisions between ultra-conservatives and more traditional GOP lawmakers have left them at a loss over who should be in charge.
